reviewText: excellent condition of dvds, great movies, good video quality.

The first movie on this disc is fairly enjoyable with attractive women in various scenes with the annoying main character. The second movie goes from sex to horror movie gore and ruins the whole mood. Don't waste your money.

This movie was not at all what I expected. I thought it would be dull and predictable with a dash of clumsy obliqueness; I couldn't have been more wrong. It was funny, charming, exotic and naughty with just the right dash of impropriety. I loved it!!!!!!!!
